data.description: Welcome FOLKS to your DREAM RETIREMENT HOME nestled in the peaceful and highly sought after community of Polo Park in Davenport. GORGEOUS does not fully describe this property!! This home sits on a Corner Lot offering a clear and relaxing view. It features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, a covered carport, two private sheds and a parking space for your golf cart! Inside, enjoy an incredible split bedroom plan, remodeled bathrooms, new laminate floors, an indoor laundry room, ceiling fans in every bedroom, generously sized living room, kitchen & dining area just perfect for entertaining and family 'get togethers'. Hold on, there is more, the enclosed side porch with A/C and trees view, is the perfect spot in the house to relax in the company of a good book and a cup of coffee! In this home you can live like you're on vacation year round w/all Polo Park offers including, but not limited to Golf, a Pro shop, 2 Heated Community Pools, an expansive Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Game Room, Library, Horseshoes, Tennis, Pickleball & Shuffleboard courts, all of this for low HOA fees of $60 a month! Isn’t that great?? This wonderful 55+ community also enjoys a great location directly off Hwy 27, just minutes from 192 and easy access to I-4, Theme Disney Parks, Grocery Stores, Medical Facilities, Restaurants, Shopping Centers & much more! Don’t wait! Ask your agent to arrange a viewing today! This home has endless potential and is waiting for a loving new owner ..... NEW ROOF from 2017 / Tiedowns fully updated in compliance with FHA regulations on 2018, and NEW A/C and Ducts from 2021. BRING YOUR OFFER -SELLER IS MOTIVATED
